data.description: Exciting chance to own a remarkable, custom-built home! Impeccably maintained 2-acre oasis in the heart of vibrant Shoreview. This home is a true masterpiece, exceeding all expectations with extraordinary construction details. Get ready to be amazed by its Austrian-inspired design and over 10,000 sq ft of luxurious living space, including a heated garage and detached building. Enjoy the pinnacle of main floor living with a captivating open concept kitchen and a lavish Master Suite. Discover abundant storage and heated floors throughout, plus a wealth of amenities like a 4-season porch, sauna, workshop, greenhouse, and multiple balconies. Located in the acclaimed Mounds View School system and just minutes away from major routes 694 and 35. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Explore floor plans, construction details, and more in the supplements. Seize your dream of owning a magnificent property in the heart of Shoreview!
